    description: "Sugar for the common case of auditioning or committing to ONE lane across the group's whole range: sets the comp to a single full-range segment on `laneId`, equivalent to calling take_set_comp with one segment spanning the group's entire extent. Use this for 'just play take 3 all the way through' before reaching for take_set_comp's per-range picking. Shares take_set_comp's undo-coalescing, so repeated quick swaps while auditioning collapse into one undo step. Returns `{group, clips}`.",
